data.description: This beautiful home welcomes you with a nice size porch, inside you will find a spacious foyer area with the first two bedrooms in the front. Great Rm give you the open floor plan perfect for entertaining with a fireplace with gas logs, you will also find arches and a vaulted ceiling, french doors to oversized deck (18x12). This home has a lot of natural lighting all throughout the home. The owners suite is also located on the main floor where it overlooks the nice size fenced back yard with plenty of privacy. Upstairs you will find HUGE bedroom with a private bath.. SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED ; priced to sell
